= About =

This script makes gpg-encrypted backups of your bitcoin wallet.

= How to use =

1. Make script executable: chmod +x backup_wallet.sh
2. Change the settings in the upper part to point to the correct files and gpg-keys.
3. Insert the correct commands to transfer the backup to a safe location.
4. Run on a regular basis. If possible, use cron/anacron/systemd to run. Make sure
   your backup commands can run unattended and without asking for passwords.
